		<ul>
			<li>Add as many video highlights as you want</li>
			<li>Custom link to track clicks to your profile</li>
			<li>Increased exposure to college coaches around the entire country</li>
			<li>$30 off subscription forever, offer valid until December 1st</li>
			<br>
			<div style="border-top:1px solid rgba(91,192,222,.3);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(91,192,222,.3);">
				<h5>Usual: <span style="text-decoration:line-through;">$200/Year</span></h5>
